Module 3 — Prompt Engineering Notes 📝

1. Prompt Engineering kya hai?
AI se sahi output nikalne ki skill — specific, clear, detailed prompt = better output!

2. Zero Shot
Koi example nahi dete — seedha question puchho
python  "Classify this as positive or negative: 'Great phone!'"

3. Few Shot
Pehle examples dete hain — AI pattern seekhta hai
python"Good phone → Positive
 Bad phone  → Negative
 Great phone → ???"

4. Format Control
AI ko explicitly batao — kitna, kaisa, kis format mein
python"Tell me 3 facts in 1 line each. Reply in one word only."

5. System Prompt
AI ka permanent behaviour set karo — ek baar likho, hamesha kaam kare
python{"role": "system", "content": "You are a strict teacher..."}

6. Chain of Thought (CoT)
AI ki reasoning visible karo — complex problems verify karne ke liye
python"Think step by step."
Best tarika — system prompt mein daalo:
python{"role": "system", "content": "Always think step by step."}

7. Structured Output (JSON)
Production apps ke liye — AI ka output directly code mein use karo
python{"role": "system", "content": "Always respond in JSON only."}
Output use karna:
pythonimport json
data = json.loads(response.choices[0].message.content)
data["name"]  # seedha value nikalo

8. Teen Ka Combo — Production Ready:
System Prompt → AI ka behaviour 👔
CoT           → AI ki reasoning 🧠
JSON          → AI ka output    📦

Golden Rules:

Specific likho — vague prompt = vague output
Format batao — AI mind reader nahi hai
System prompt use karo — baar baar likhne ki zaroorat nahi
CoT lagao — jab reasoning verify karni ho
JSON use karo — jab output code mein use karna ho